title: NFL ATL: 2014 Draft Preview Spectacular!
itunes:title: NFL ATL: 2014 Draft Preview Spectacular!
description:
A room with a couple of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal and Chris Wesseling -- previews the 2014 NFL Draft.  With the help of Matt “Money” Smith in studio -- and heroes in exile, Dan Hanzus and Marc Sessler, via hologram from New York -- Gregg and Chris break down everything you need to know about Johnny Manziel, Jadeveon Clowney and the offseason’s marquee event.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
